---
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';
import AnchorNav from '../components/AnchorNav.astro';
import WorkshopCard from '../components/WorkshopCard.astro';
import CourseCard from '../components/CourseCard.astro';

const workshops = (await getCollection('workshops')).sort((a, b) => a.data.order - b.data.order);
const courses = (await getCollection('courses')).sort((a, b) => a.data.order - b.data.order);
const communityWorkshops = workshops.filter((w) => w.data.track === 'community');
const careerWorkshops = workshops.filter((w) => w.data.track === 'career');

const delivery = [
  { title: 'Partnership delivery', body: 'We come to your organization, your space, your community.', icon: 'ph:handshake-bold', chip: 'bg-brand-red text-white' },
  { title: 'Public schedule', body: 'Open sessions anyone can register for.', icon: 'ph:calendar-dots-bold', chip: 'bg-brand-blue text-white' },
  { title: 'Custom engagements', body: 'Tailored programs for specific groups, industries, or cohorts.', icon: 'ph:sliders-horizontal-bold', chip: 'bg-brand-gold text-ink' },
];
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Workshops & Courses | Digital Skills & AI Training in Vancouver"
  description="Technology workshops and multi-session courses built around real outcomes — digital confidence, online safety, AI workflows, and more. Vancouver and area."
>
  <Hero title="Programs built around<br />real outcomes.">
    <Fragment slot="lead">
      <p>There is a technology gap — between what today's tools can do and what anyone has time to figure out. Our workshops and courses close it: we cut through the noise, focus on the skills you actually need for your work and your life, and build the confidence to use them. Delivered in Vancouver and the surrounding area. Accommodating all skill levels.</p>
    </Fragment>
  </Hero>

  <section class="container-wide py-16 md:py-24">
    <SectionHeading title="How our programs work.">
      <p>Every program starts from the same promise: we filter the noise. New tools launch every week, and you do not need most of them. We teach the ones that matter for your goals — in plain language, at your pace, shaped around your community. You leave with skills you will actually use and the confidence to keep going on your own.</p>
    </SectionHeading>

    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      <a href="#workshops" class="flex h-full flex-col rounded-[14px] border-2 border-ink bg-ink p-8 text-cream transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 md:p-10">
        <span class="flex h-16 w-16 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-gold text-ink text-4xl"><Icon name="ph:chalkboard-teacher-bold" /></span>
        <h3 class="mt-6 text-h2">Workshops</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 flex-1 text-body-lg">Single sessions or short series, designed to deliver immediately useful skills.</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-body font-bold text-brand-gold">90 min–half day &middot; single or series &middot; in-person or online</p>
        <span class="mt-6 font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em]">See workshops &darr;</span>
      </a>
      <a href="#courses" class="flex h-full flex-col rounded-[14px] border-2 border-ink bg-brand-gold p-8 text-ink transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 md:p-10">
        <span class="flex h-16 w-16 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-ink text-brand-gold text-4xl"><Icon name="ph:graduation-cap-bold" /></span>
        <h3 class="mt-6 text-h2">Courses</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 flex-1 text-body-lg">Multi-session programs that build something functional by the end.</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-body font-bold">4–6 hours &middot; multi-session &middot; delivered in partnership</p>
        <span class="mt-6 font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em]">See courses &darr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      {delivery.map((d) => (
        <div class="h-full rounded-[14px] border-2 border-ink bg-white p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class:list={["flex h-14 w-14 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full text-3xl", d.chip]}><Icon name={d.icon} /></span>
            <h3 class="text-h3">{d.title}</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-body text-body-muted">{d.body}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 rounded-[14px] border-2 border-ink bg-blush p-8 md:flex md:items-center md:justify-between md:gap-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h3 class="text-h3">Funding is available right now.</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-body text-body-muted">Provincial and federal funding covers many of these programs — especially digital skills and AI upskilling for specific communities. We help you identify what applies and work through it alongside you.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6 shrink-0 md:mt-0"><Button href="/partnerships">Explore Funded Partnerships</Button></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <AnchorNav anchors={[{ label: 'Workshops', href: '#workshops' }, { label: 'Courses', href: '#courses' }, { label: 'Looking for Something Else?', href: '#more' }]} />

  <section id="workshops" class="container-wide py-16 md:py-24">
    <SectionHeading title="Workshops." />

    <h3 class="text-h3 mt-8 mb-6">Track 1 &middot; Community and Everyday Life</h3>
    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      {communityWorkshops.map((w) => <WorkshopCard workshop={w.data} slug={w.id} />)}
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-h3 mt-12 mb-6">Track 2 &middot; Career, Work, and Growth</h3>
    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      {careerWorkshops.map((w) => <WorkshopCard workshop={w.data} slug={w.id} />)}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="courses" class="container-wide py-16 md:py-24">
    <SectionHeading title="Courses.">
      <p>Multi-session programs for organizations and individuals ready to go deeper and come away with something they can actually use. Every course is delivered in partnership — we build alongside your team so the skills and systems stay with your organization long after it ends.</p>
    </SectionHeading>

    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      {courses.map((c) => <CourseCard course={c.data} slug={c.id} />)}
    </div>

    <p class="mt-8 text-body text-body-muted">Additional course tracks are in development. <a href="/contact" class="font-bold text-brand-red hover:text-ink">Talk to us about a custom course</a> for your community or sector.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="more" class="container-wide py-16 md:py-24">
    <SectionHeading title="Looking for something else?">
      <p>If these are not quite the right fit, there is more — one-on-one tutoring and mentorship, small group instruction, team training, and deeper technical topics for people ready for that level.</p>
      <p>More workshops are in development across additional topics and industries. If you have something specific in mind, reach out. The answer is probably yes.</p>
    </SectionHeading>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-6">
      <Button href="/contact">Get in Touch</Button>
      <a href="mailto:holler@weallrize.ca" class="font-bold text-brand-red hover:text-ink">holler@weallrize.ca</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
